VALUES ('954f4cb1-7cdd-404c-a30d-cb1c235db27e', 'Based on the texts, how would the author of Text 2 most likely respond to the claim in Text 1 that fluency follows almost on its own through immersion?', 'Text 1
To learn a new language, immersion is essential. Surrounded by native speakers, a learner absorbs grammar and vocabulary naturally, the way a child does, without dry drills or memorization. Travel abroad, and fluency follows almost on its own.

Text 2
I lived overseas for two years and barely improved until I sat down with a grammar book each night. Immersion gave me confidence to speak, but it was deliberate, structured study that fixed my errors. Exposure alone is not enough; one must also practice with intention.', NULL, '[{"id":"A","text":"Immersion played no role whatsoever in the author''s learning.","is_correct":false,"explanation":"Contradicts Text 2, which credits immersion with building confidence."},{"id":"B","text":"Living abroad alone guarantees fluency for any learner.","is_correct":false,"explanation":"Reverses Text 2''s point that exposure alone is not enough."},{"id":"C","text":"Deliberate, structured study is also needed, not just exposure.","is_correct":true,"explanation":"Correct: Text 2 says exposure alone is not enough and one must practice with intention."},{"id":"D","text":"Grammar books are the only useful tool for learning a language.","is_correct":false,"explanation":"Too narrow; Text 2 values immersion for confidence alongside study."}]'::jsonb, 'C', 'Step 1 — Find Text 2''s claim
Text 2 concludes that {{yellow:Exposure alone is not enough; one must also practice with intention}}.
Step 2 — Apply to Text 1
Because Text 2 insists on deliberate study, it would qualify Text 1''s claim that fluency arrives almost on its own.
Distractor analysis:
- A: Contradicts Text 2, which says immersion gave confidence.
- B: Reverses Text 2''s main argument.
- D: Too narrow—Text 2 still values immersion.', 'What does Text 2 say must accompany exposure?', 'Craft and Structure', 'Cross-Text Connections', 'reading_writing', 'craft', 'CTC', NULL, 'easy', false, 'SAT', 'multiple_choice', true, true, 'scholaris_ai', '{"generator":"scholaris_ai_v1","model":"gemma-4-26b-a4b-it","original":true,"explanation_v2":true}'::jsonb, now(), now())
ON CONFLICT (id) DO NOTHING;
